##脚本
```sql
CREATE CACHED TABLE "PUBLIC"."USERS"(
    "ID" INTEGER GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY(START WITH 1 RESTART WITH 33) NOT NULL,
    "ACCOUNT_ID" CHARACTER VARYING(100),
    "NAME" CHARACTER VARYING(50),
    "TOKEN" CHARACTER(36),
    "GMT_CREATE" BIGINT,
    "GMT_MODIFIED" BIGINT
)
```
